         <abstract id="aspace_6185238fb1896ec714ff5e1e27b00486">Diary, account book, financial and legal papers, and photocopies of material relating to the Towner and Tyler families of Branford, Connecticut. Solomon and Isaac Tyler's shipping interests and John Edwin Towner's Civil War diary are significant materials in the collection.</abstract>
         <origination label="Creator">
            <famname rules="aacr" source="local">
               <part localtype="agent_family">Towner family</part>
            </famname>
         </origination>
      </did>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_467d7047aa79901616c68116d4b6f09e">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Deposited by L. Eugene Towner, 1960. Final gift by Lester N. Towner, 1966.</p>
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_227dc4002bf2543129c12024e7ff9450">
